	$this->setselectdomain($domainname)
list domains icon:  op=selectdomain

de-select domain link: http://jasonubuntu2/ehcp/?op=deselectdomain
Other operations link: http://jasonubuntu2/ehcp/index.php?op=otheroperations calls $this->otheroperations
    sets homepage template to either homepage_reseller_other or homepage_serveradmin_other



list subdomains icon: op=subdomains
add subdomain icon: op=addsubdomain  
edit domain aliases: http://jasonubuntu2/ehcp/?op=editdomainaliases
list custom http: http://jasonubuntu2/ehcp/?op=customhttp
add custom http: http://jasonubuntu2/ehcp/?op=addcustomhttp
edit apache template: http://jasonubuntu2/ehcp/?op=editapachetemplate
edit dns template: http://jasonubuntu2/ehcp/?op=editdnstemplate
list password protected directories: http://jasonubuntu2/ehcp/?op=directories
add password protected directories: http://jasonubuntu2/ehcp/?op=adddirectory



list databases: http://jasonubuntu2/ehcp/?op=domainop&action=listdb
add mysql database and user: http://jasonubuntu2/ehcp/?op=addmysqldb

add mysql database to existing user: http://jasonubuntu2/ehcp/?op=addmysqldbtouser
add mysql user to existing database: http://jasonubuntu2/ehcp/?op=dbadduser


delete account: http://jasonubuntu2/ehcp/?op=deletedomain
activate/deactivate domain: http://jasonubuntu2/ehcp/?op=editdomain
change settings: http://jasonubuntu2/ehcp/?op=domainsettings
